title: DUNLOP typeface identification…
content:
Anybody know what the title font is for Dunlop brand?

I know the sub font is Eurostile - slanted and squashed.

But the head?

[http://www.dunlopsports.com/](http://web.archive.org/web/20131221141356/http:/www.dunlopsports.com/)

Its the slab serifed, main version.

Thanks in advance!!

Nick
